text: _Team *The Swift Exit* joined the shared channel_

Hey everyone. We'll kick this off with one of our all time favourites that helped us develop a whole new *entrepreneurial mindset* and applied that to *forging our career path* - LinkedIn’s Reid Hoffman and Ben Casnocha write at length about this concept in their book “<https://www.amazon.co.uk/Start-up-You-Future-Yourself-Transform/dp/1847940803|The start-up of you>” … it hits the nail on the head! _[Note: This is NOT an affiliate link … just a bloody good book!]_).

If you're more of a podcast person and you haven't heard of Tim Ferris, you've got a whole new world to explore on his website (<https://tim.blog/>). Check it out for all things career related, entrepreneurial motivation and otherwise!
